This README file contains information on the contents of the meta-bl808-mmc-clock layer.

Please see the corresponding sections below for details.

Dependencies
============

  URI: https://github.com/ErmakovDmitriy/meta-bl808/tree/mickledore
  branch: mickledore

Patches
=======

Please submit any patches against the meta-bl808-mmc-clock layer to Dmitrii Ermakov <demonihin@gmail.com> or as GitHub pull requests

Table of Contents
=================

  I. Adding the meta-bl808-mmc-clock layer to your build
 II. Misc


I. Adding the meta-bl808-mmc-clock layer to your build
=================================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-bl808-mmc-clock'

II. Misc
========

This layer applies SDHC bus clock tuning patch from https://github.com/openbouffalo/buildroot_bouffalo/pull/59 to Yocto meta-bl808.

It allows starting BL808 based boards with more SD card models
which have problems with the default bus clock settings.